{"tid":1131670,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/ Steam] Arma 3 武裝行動 冷戰德國DLC上架","createTime":"2019-04-29T21:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T07:15:49.000Z","uid":164307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"75ef3037f89a4107ba751b4785056958b62c3a06","tid":1131670,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T21:07:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/4SqRekKDgLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4SqRekKDgLc&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=6496a487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4SqRekKDgLc</a></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n官方介紹翻譯:</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>內容</strong></ins></span><br />\n歡迎! 係時侯回到冷戰時期。包含極大量既新原創內容，Global Mobilization - Cold War Germany Creator DLC帶你走入80年代東西德嘅衝突之中。踏入裝甲戰爭，面對一班寧死不屈嘅敵軍，準備隨時數量遠超過你？體驗戰事由步兵垂死掙扎到裝甲車增援，又或者攻入具象徵嘅德國邊境威脅敵方拱手相讓？你究竟會為鐵幕(Iron Curtain)邊一方而戰呢？除咗東西德軍隊以外，你亦可以選擇丹麥軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>重點介紹</strong></ins></span><br />\n<strong>韋弗林根地形 (Weferlingen Terrain)</strong><br />\n位於德國北部嘅平原，地圖實用面積約419km&sup2;，喺官方暫時為止發放最大嘅地圖。呢張圖係依照1983年現實韋弗林根而建造，當中運用咗許多新元素，保證帶比玩家換然一新嘅體驗。除咗叢林以外，官方亦首次發佈有冰天雪地既塲境。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJJfQZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJJfQZY.jpg&h=c1b82cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>42輛新載具</strong><br />\n<em>西德</em>:  Leopard 1A1A1 &amp; 1A3主戰坦克， M113裝甲運兵車，FlakPz 1A1防空坦克......<br />\n<em>東德</em>: T-55A主戰坦克，BMP-1裝甲運兵車，SPW-40偵察車......<br />\n<em>平民</em>: Typ 1200德國大眾汽車60-70年代甲蟲車......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mK4KKjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmK4KKjG.jpg&h=5ad4caeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>21種新武器</strong><br />\n<em>西德</em>: G3系列步槍，MG3機槍，MP2A1衝鋒槍，P1手槍......<br />\n<em>東德</em>: KM-72德製AK-47步槍，PRK-74輕機槍，PKM機槍，RPG-7反載具火箭筒......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZVNG7R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZVNG7R.jpg&h=85576dc1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong>其他</strong><br />\n-10個個人故事任務&quot;State Scarlet&quot;<br />\n-17個多人遊玩塲境<br />\n<br />\n詳細內容:<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1042220/Arma_3_Creator_DLC_Global_Mobilization__Cold_War_Germany/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1042220%2FArma_3_Creator_DLC_Global_Mobilization__Cold_War_Germany%2F&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=d8032a7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1042220/Arma_3_Creator_DLC_Global_Mobilization__Cold_War_Germany/</a><br />\n<br />\n假如你對多人軍事模擬有興趣，歡迎加入我哋BOWHK<br />\nDiscord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/tSqyNZY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FtSqyNZY&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=80625cfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/tSqyNZY</a>"},{"pid":"398346652643a1f23c78728b59779d838f306d8b","tid":1131670,"uid":173088,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"香港有一隊叫SSHK<br />\n人地人又多，做野又認真。你地人咁少不如你入埋佢地果隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sshkarma/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsshkarma%2F&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=1a68193c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sshkarma/</a>"},{"pid":"196c05141b40b943fc17313f99019ce12694bf74","tid":1131670,"uid":49094,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:49:42.000Z","msg":"出德國都唔出g36<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897ca3c36c89a85e43adc130d6